reviews.text: Small local restaurant, friendly staff but the coffee was a little off in my opinion.  I got the sweet and sour chicken, it was crispy, tangy and just the right amount of sweetness.  I think it was part of a set meal.  Don't forget to add a friend egg for 5hkd(I think) nothing special but all 5 of the friend eggs for our party had just the right amount of yolk run.
Very good little restaurant. Health food, very fresh ingredient. One of the best hole in the wall
resonable price and very yummy

Pleasant dining experience with warm hospitality. The restaurant was running as family restaurant, where the sons were helping as waiters and the parents works behind the bar table or in the kitchen. The food are good and healthy, low oil, low salt and low sugar menu was available. The service is fabulous and as I said, it has the special warm hospitality as family restaurant. However the place is a bit dirty and sticky, so a star was taken off.
Very delicious Chinese food, reasonable price, unlimited rice and soup, we finish the meal before remember to put the comment here!
